<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><rss version="2.0"><channel><title>老麦笔记 - Mastodon 系列</title><description>这里是老麦的个人博客，分享生活、热爱生活、享受生活，主打真实与平淡。 // Mastodon 系列订阅</description><link>https://www.iamlm.com/</link><item><title>老麦于2026/02/16的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116080914443345999/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116080914443345999/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;突然间很是感慨，只因今年的除夕夜终于不用在那个坚守了十多年的地方打卡咯。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.laomai.org/media_attachments/files/116/080/909/646/874/445/original/1254fe4f4b9f1de3.png&quot; alt=&quot;麦家围夜市1&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://cdn.laomai.org/media_attachments/files/116/080/910/203/341/700/original/95103814ab39a844.png&quot; alt=&quot;麦家围夜市2&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 16 Feb 2026 15:03:07 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/02/15的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116076071859083217/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116076071859083217/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;今晚和老婆小酌微醺，聊了很多心里话。生活不必一直紧绷，偶尔慢下来，就是最好的调剂。&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Feb 2026 18:31:35 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/02/15的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116073820653357902/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116073820653357902/</guid><description>&lt;p class=&quot;quote-inline&quot;&gt;RE: &lt;a href=&quot;https://m.laomai.org/@laomai/115631758684364762&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;m.laomai.org/@laomai/1156317586843&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;64762&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;想要解决这个问题只需在动画里添加一个属性 fill: &amp;#39;forwards&amp;#39;&lt;br /&gt;这样子动画结束后，保持动画最后一帧的样式。&lt;br /&gt;如果没有这个属性，浏览器会把 clip-path 恢复为动画前的状态（circle(0px)），然后把 ViewTransition 图层移除，在这个过渡层消失时就会出现视觉断层，就会出现闪烁问题。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/docs/Web/CSS/Reference/Properties/animation-fill-mode&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;developer.mozilla.org/zh-CN/do&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;cs/Web/CSS/Reference/Properties/animation-fill-mode&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Sun, 15 Feb 2026 08:59:05 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/02/10的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116048190519552433/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116048190519552433/</guid><description>&lt;p class=&quot;quote-inline&quot;&gt;RE: &lt;a href=&quot;https://nofan.xyz/@j_will/116029625817298933&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot; translate=&quot;no&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;https://&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;ellipsis&quot;&gt;nofan.xyz/@j_will/116029625817&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;invisible&quot;&gt;298933&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;收藏&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 10 Feb 2026 20:21:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/02/09的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116039643498067181/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116039643498067181/</guid><pubDate>Mon, 09 Feb 2026 08:07:23 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/02/06的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/116025063991672655/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/116025063991672655/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;突然觉得很「累」。🫩&lt;/p&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Feb 2026 18:19:37 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>老麦于2026/01/21的嘟文</title><link>https://www.iamlm.com/says/115931485956537006/</link><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.iamlm.com/says/115931485956537006/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;这次降温降得有点猛。🥶🥶🥶&lt;/p&gt;</descri